column3: You have business with me, adventurer?
I'm the harbormaster here at Vesper Bay. My responsibility is to ensure that all is smooth sailing, and at all times.
I pride myself on maintaining the best facility on the mainland. Ours is a bustling port, and without sound management, things would very quickly run to chaos.
Vesper Bay was built only a number of years ago, but, in a short span of time, it's grown into the premier ocean gateway to Ul'dah.
That even the largest vessels might find mooring here, large-scale excavation was undertaken to deepen the seabed. 'Twas a costly venture made possible only through the generosity of Lord Lolorito.
It's to him that our port owes its prosperity. There's no shortage of opportunities to be had by enterprising individuals.
What kind of place is this?
